{
  "stem": "23942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In other words, she wanted-- each time I came into her house she was nice to me, but she also took some water from-- there was on the wall like a container.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know if this water was from the church or they made holy, whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she tried to sprinkle me, like, you know, and to bap-- not bap-- One day she said, you know, after she knew me awhile she said, you know, I'll take you to the priest and he'll baptize you and he'll make you into a real Catholic little child.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this part I blocked out of my mind for 40 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't remember it till I went back to Poland and I met this Jewish woman who was born a Jewish woman, but she is a Catholic.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She practices the Catholic religion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was born into a Jewish family, and I found her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she reminded me something that I'd blocked out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she told me about me what lady, the old Lady Gdynska told her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that part I didn't remember till I went back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she told her after I left Grodzisko they were talking about me, how smart I was to survive, how I managed to do all this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When the war ended they knew that I made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know how, but they knew I made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they didn't understand how I made it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That I was so bright that I did it against all odds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she reminded, this lady, this Jewish Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She told her that I one day I came and she wanted to baptize me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I forgot about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She wanted to take me to the priest and baptize me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I forgot about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
